                            <comment id="13103655" author="deinspanjer" created="Tue, 13 Sep 2011 14:25:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This script deletes regions on a live table. The only thing it doesn&apos;t currently do is split regions that are partially within the start / end key range.  I would love it if someone could take a crack at putting that enhancement in this or writing a separate script to do it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tested with a few test clusters in various conditions and then used this script to delete thousands of old regions from our large production table.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13448204" author="lhofhansl" created="Tue, 4 Sep 2012 23:43:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the script Ophir. I&apos;m marking this as DUP of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5504&quot; title=&quot;Online Merge&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5504&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5504&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I linked back to this issue from there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
